The paper deals with weight initialization in deep neural networks, specifically in long short-term memory (LSTM) networks. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper also applies the proposed method to time series regression and disease progression modeling, which suggests it could belong to computer vision (cs.CV) or computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories.
